fields.name: Butter

fields.name: Bacon
fields.description: Our hand selected and trimmed prime cuts of bacon. Quality Checked - Created for Taste and Flavour. No Artificial Colours or Flavours

fields.storage: Keep refrigerated. Once opened, keep refrigerated and consume within 2 days. Do not exceed the Use By date. Suitable for freezing. Freeze before date mark shown and consume within 1 month. Defrost and consume on day of defrost. Once defrosted, do not refreeze

fields.name: Pork Sausages
fields.description: 12 premium pork sausages. Gluten Free. A Passion for Quality. With a Pinch of Classic Spices. No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Hydrogenated Fat
fields.ingredients: Pork (90%), Water, Rice Flour, Salt, Chickpea Flour, Spices, Stabiliser (Diphosphates), Preservative (Sodium Metabisulphite), Flavouring, Cornflour (contains Sulphites), Antioxidant (Ascorbic Acid), Dextrose (contains Sulphites), Sausage Casing [Calcium Alginate]
fields.storage:
Keep refrigerated. Do not exceed the use by date. Store uncooked meat covered and lower in the fridge than cooked meat.
Suitable for freezing. Freeze before date mark shown and consume within 1 month.
Defrost and consume on day of defrost.
Once defrosted, do not refreeze
